{"questionId":"10065","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"S\">\n  <mi>S</mi>\n</math></span><sub><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"n\">\n  <mi>n</mi>\n</math></span></sub>&nbsp;be the sum of the first <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"n\">\n  <mi>n</mi>\n</math></span> terms of the arithmetic series 2 + 4 + 6 + ….</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let <strong><em>M </em></strong>= <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1&amp;2 \\\\   0&amp;1  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>It may now be assumed that <strong><em>M</em></strong><sup><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"n\">\n  <mi>n</mi>\n</math></span></sup>&nbsp;= <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1&amp;{2n} \\\\   0&amp;1  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n              <mi>n</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>,&nbsp;for <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"n\">\n  <mi>n</mi>\n</math></span> ≥ 4. The sum <strong><em>T</em></strong><sub><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"n\">\n  <mi>n</mi>\n</math></span></sub>&nbsp;is defined by</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><strong><em>T</em></strong><sub><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"n\">\n  <mi>n</mi>\n</math></span></sub> = <strong><em>M</em></strong><sup>1</sup>&nbsp;+ <strong><em>M</em></strong><sup>2</sup>&nbsp;+ <strong><em>M</em></strong><sup>3</sup>&nbsp;+ ... + <strong><em>M</em></strong><sup><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"n\">\n  <mi>n</mi>\n</math></span></sup>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Find&nbsp;<strong><em>T</em></strong><sub>4</sub>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong><em>T</em></strong><sub>4</sub> = <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1&amp;2 \\\\   0&amp;1  \\end{array}} \\right) + \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1&amp;4 \\\\   0&amp;1  \\end{array}} \\right) + \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1&amp;6 \\\\   0&amp;1  \\end{array}} \\right) + \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1&amp;8 \\\\   0&amp;1  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>4</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>8</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp;(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>=&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  4&amp;{20} \\\\   0&amp;4  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>4</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>20</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>4</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1A1&nbsp; &nbsp; N3</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"10065","referenceCode":"EXM.2.AHL.TZ0.7c.ii","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Find T4.","paper":"2","level":"HL","questionNumber":"c.ii","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","AHL 1.14—Introduction to matrices"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}